para_trans: With regard to amending the Government Decision on recognition of new subjects / courses, additional batches, faculties under the extension for the academic year 2024-25.
Department of Higher and Technical Education

Corrigendum: As per the recommendation of the Survey Non-Agricultural University of the State for the academic year 2024-25 as per the Government decision under reference, new subjects / courses, additional batches, new faculty have been sanctioned under expansion in the existing colleges. Accordingly, Anand Charitable Institution under Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar Marathwada University, Aashti managed Andrao Dhonde Sh Babaji College, Kada, Ta. Ashti, G. Beed College was granted affiliation for the extension of BSc Forensic Science. However, now Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar Marathwada University and Anand Charitable Trust, Ashti, have requested for modification of this order of recognition. Accordingly, the Government is giving its approval to the amendment mentioned in the following statement as the relevant Government decision needs to be amended after examining the available documents.
